#. <section class="sutta" id="sn56.59"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.59:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.59:0.2"
msgid "6. Abhisamayavagga"
msgstr "6. Comprehension"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.59:0.3"
msgid "59. Paṭhamapabbatūpamasutta"
msgstr "59. A Mountain (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.464"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.59:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, puriso himavato pabbatarājassa satta sāsapamattiyo "
"pāsāṇasakkharā upanikkhipeyya."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, suppose a person was to place seven pebbles the size of mustard "
"seeds on the Himalayas, the king of mountains."

msgctxt "sn56.59:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn56.59:1.3"
msgid ""
"katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ—yā vā satta sāsapamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā "
"upanikkhittā, ayaṃ vā himavā pabbatarājā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Which is more: the seven pebbles the size of mustard seeds, or the "
"Himalayas, the king of mountains?”"

msgctxt "sn56.59:1.4"
msgid ""
"“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ, yadidaṃ—himavā pabbatarājā; appamattikā satta "
"sāsapamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā upanikkhittā."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, the Himalayas, the king of mountains, is certainly more. The seven "
"pebbles the size of mustard seeds are tiny."

msgctxt "sn56.59:1.5"
msgid ""
"Saṅkhampi na upenti, upanidhampi na upenti, kalabhāgampi na upenti "
"himavantaṃ pabbatarājānaṃ upanidhāya satta sāsapamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā "
"upanikkhittā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Compared to the Himalayas, they can’t be reckoned or compared, they’re not "
"even a fraction.”"

msgctxt "sn56.59:1.6"
msgid "“Evameva kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa … pe …"
msgstr "“In the same way, for a noble disciple …"

msgctxt "sn56.59:1.7"
msgid "yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.59:1.8"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
